<!-- module text -->
<div id="text-2-1-0-1" class="module module-text text-2-1-0-1   ">
	
	
	<p style="text-align: left;">It&#8217;s 1862. You are hand-digging through layers of soggy, worthless, frustrating gravel, hoping and praying the next shovel-stroke will expose a fortune in gold. Everyone says it&#8217;s crazy, but there&#8217;s too much at stake. Then, just when the outcome seems impossibly bleak, at a depth of 52 feet the ground begins to pay. The lead is struck, and the greatest creek side placer gold deposit the world has ever seen is suddenly yours for the taking.</p><h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #c4990c;"><a style="color: #c4990c;" title="About Us" href="http://www.barkerville.ca/about-us/">This is Barkerville&#8217;s story.</a></span></h4>
	</div>
<!-- /module text -->

