        <div class="module-feature-content">
                            <h3 class="module-feature-title">
                                            <a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/places-to-stay/" >
                           
                        Places to Stay
                                                </a>
                                    </h3>
            
            <p style="text-align: left;">It can take more than one day to explore everything Barkerville has to offer. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;re one of the few historic sites in Canada where guests can stay overnight, on-site! With 3 bed & breakfasts and 3 large campgrounds, as well as additional hotels, motels, cabins and more in nearby Wells, on beautiful Bowron Lake, at Cottonwood House Historic Site, or the city of Quesnel&#8230; why not plan stay awhile for the ultimate Barkerville experience?</p>        </div>

            </div>
